# Agent Trace Log - Intent-Code Traceability
# This file records every file modification with intent linkage
# Format: JSON Lines (one JSON object per line)
# 
# Each entry contains:
# - id: UUID
# - timestamp: ISO 8601
# - intent_id: The active intent ID
# - mutation_class: AST_REFACTOR | INTENT_EVOLUTION | READ_ONLY
# - files: Array of file modifications with content_hash
#
# This file is append-only. Do not manually edit.
